RuntimeFunction previously fell through to the base Callable override
which returns true for kCCBuiltins, causing arguments to be skipped from
the Torque stack and triggering 'wrong argument types' at type-instruction
time. RuntimeFunction now overrides ShouldBeInlined to return false for
